		Sunset: {
			DisplayName: Sunset
			Tooltip: "[Stage]"
			DisplayNameS0: Sunset
			TooltipS0:
				'''
				The crimson spear, burning with twilight.
				Left-click — unleash a four-strike volley, each spear detonating into a miniature starburst.
				Right-click — raise the spear to the heavens, gathering the light of every star,
				As a newborn sun, collapsing into a cataclysmic explosion.

				— This is the sight he cherished most,
				made beautiful by her presence, burning in his grasp.
				At the very end, he crushed the cosmos into a single sun,
				only to share one final sunset with her.

				① When carried alongside other auxiliary weapons,  
