				“Please, don’t forget me.”

				① When carried alongside other auxiliary weapons,  
				   the spear brands its wielder with searing flames;  
				   but when borne alone, it cleanses every curse in silence.  

				② The firmer the defense, the lighter the wound—  
				   true protection and the power of renewal grow ever stronger.  

				③ When defense falls to zero, with only wings and mobility trinkets to hold the sky,  
				   the spear awakens, bestowing a ruinous boon:  
				   damage, penetration, and critical chance surge,  
				   speed sharpens, yet immunity and endurance are stripped away,  
				   until the final strike blooms with fourfold annihilation.
				'''
			DisplayNameS2: Concept
