				'''
				The silver-gold spear, manifestation of dominion.
				Switching to this form — ten fragments of inspiration rise and orbit your body.
				Left-click — whirl the spear in a deadly dance, then raise it high;
				a vast magic circle brands the enemy, gnawing at its soul,
