				Every thirty shards merge into a colossal timebreaker,
				crashing down from above to shatter space itself.

				— This is his true power:
				beyond all limits, ruling over everything.
				Even “concepts” themselves bow at the tip of his spear.

				① When carried alongside other auxiliary weapons,  
				   the spear brands its wielder with searing flames;  
