		ShadowJav: {
			DisplayName: Infinity Boundless
			Tooltip:
				'''
				Left-click to throw the lance.
				After flying a short distance, it splits into 2–4 random lances at its position,
				only selecting lances from this mod (excluding developer weapons).
				The splitting lances ignore the original lance's limitations (e.g., Pearlwood Spear's one-lance limit).
				The main lance continues flying after splitting, piercing infinitely.
				Right-click to shoot a lance that tracks and attaches to enemies,
				summoning random lances around it during its attachment.
