			[c/ff94b: Therefore, what you need to do is to maintain a healthy state as much as possible while ensuring survival]
			[c/ff94b: According to relevant literature, almost no one was able to survive the fourth attack.]
			[c/ff94b: Therefore, I have the same requirements for you]
